551
00:51:00,400 --> 00:51:02,200
Biely nos...

552
00:51:02,200 --> 00:51:05,800
- Zhao Tian Xing, poď sem!
- Hej!

553
00:51:05,800 --> 00:51:10,700
- Zostaň stáť!
- Hej! Je to na mne!

554
00:51:40,520 --> 00:51:47,770
Povedz, keď bol Malý princ uštipnutý hadom,

555
00:51:47,770 --> 00:51:51,060
